subtitleNullable: A training data set (20 images) for traffic signs. Made by János Török.
descriptionNullable:
The dataset contains 20 images that are screenshots from Google Street View. The challenge is to identify the different Traffic signs shown in the dataset.

The different classes are:

no-right-left-or-u-turn
speed-limit
road-closed
no-entry
no-stopping-no-parking
other

The original dataset was made by Török János and I used Roboflow to annotate the images manually.
